<fieldset class="howtouse line"> 
    <legend class="h1">How to use</legend>
    <ul>
        <li>Conversation will be deleted from your device after you disconnect/exit.</li>
        <li>You cannot see previous messages after re joining.</li>
        <li>You can vibrate other users phone by tapping ther name from the active online users list.</li>
        <li>On Pc, use can use Ctrl+Enter to send message.</li>
        <li>Messages will be deleted for everyone on the current chat by clicking trash icon.</li>
        <li>From 2 to 15 people can join on the same chat. You can limit the maximum peoples who can join.</li>
        <li>Session key will be expired immediately if there's no one on the chat.</li>
    </ul>
</fieldset>
